defaultDomain.content:
slots:
  disambiguation_message:
    type: unfeaturized
actions:
  - action_botfront_disambiguation
  - action_botfront_disambiguation_followup
  - action_botfront_fallback
  - action_botfront_mapping

sequence.content:
text: which account would you like to access
buttons:
  - title: checking account
    type: postback
    payload: /access_account_checking
  - title: saving account
    type: postback
    payload: /access_account_saving
text: your checking account has a balance of  XXXX.XX$
text: your savings account has XXXX.XX$
text: 'right now it is 8:00pm on Thursday January 8th 2013'

models.name: My First Model
models.config:
pipeline:
  - name: WhitespaceTokenizer
  - name: CountVectorsFeaturizer
  - name: EmbeddingIntentClassifier
  - BILOU_flag: true
    name: CRFEntityExtractor
    features:
      - [low, title, upper]
      - [low, bias, prefix5, prefix2, suffix5, suffix3, suffix2, upper, title, digit, pattern]
      - [low, title, upper]
  - name: rasa_addons.nlu.components.gazette.Gazette
  - name: EntitySynonymMapper
